{"tid":1179850,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實仲有咩可以同政府傾？","createTime":"2019-05-31T11:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T09:02:49.000Z","uid":48117,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee5a120d8082cf41a0ebe783986e3f5af7bb1413","tid":1179850,"uid":48117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MP6enMbrZbA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMP6enMbrZbA&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=47306229\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MP6enMbrZbA</a><br />\n先貼咗link先<br />\n睇完今日保安事務委員會個會<br />\n真心唔明班高官個腦諗緊啲乜<br />\n<br />\n先唔講由佢地保持慣例地頭到尾都灑緊太極<br />\n佢地係連基本對答都做唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好講班飯民、連田二少一開波條問題都要激嬲人先答咗啲似是疑非既野出來，人地係條是非題唔可以正面答咪答唔可以正面答囉，答堆野九唔搭八、重重覆覆。<br />\n<br />\n就算班高官出來對話搞公聽會又有乜野用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家香港既情況同搵個盲既人渣巴士有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n由第一次法案委員會開始之後<br />\n每次內委會、大會都有睇直播<br />\n總結感受都係一句話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家6月9一定要出來</span>"},{"pid":"4e3f418760689b096d9e80bbd6b8c0ac77ade785","tid":1179850,"uid":48117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"推，發現好多人無睇星期五個會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa187dc8454a1dde1a48ae7be28dae53a345efbd","tid":1179850,"uid":65123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pc5ZrfZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPc5ZrfZ.gif&h=a7e6ceac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f65a2aa3e9e9d24cf4fde03743c371dfdaa60e2b","tid":1179850,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T08:04:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34fd2ccb849abdc1b6abb153f73d06cd5bb3fb37","tid":1179850,"uid":48117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa187dc8454a1dde1a48ae7be28dae53